1
00:02:03,960 --> 00:02:05,880
Please invite the Father Emperor.

2
00:02:16,960 --> 00:02:18,720
I have always heard that Director Shang

3
00:02:18,880 --> 00:02:20,360
dislikes us women the most,

4
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:21,760
and that what you love listening to most

5
00:02:21,760 --> 00:02:24,160
are plays of ill-fated love and disastrous longing.

6
00:02:25,280 --> 00:02:26,600
Today, this *The Solo Saber Meeting*,

7
00:02:27,520 --> 00:02:28,240
how is it?

8
00:02:30,640 --> 00:02:31,480
Imperial Noble Consort,

9
00:02:32,920 --> 00:02:35,520
Master Konghui passed away less than seven days ago.

10
00:02:35,920 --> 00:02:37,480
Your invitation for me to enter the palace this time

11
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:39,120
is truly inappropriate.

12
00:02:41,480 --> 00:02:44,160
Who ruled that one cannot play music in great grief?

13
00:02:45,600 --> 00:02:47,000
Last night, His Majesty and I

14
00:02:47,040 --> 00:02:49,440
listened to *The Moon-Worshipping Pavilion* and *The Soul of a Love-Struck Maiden Departs*.

15
00:02:50,760 --> 00:02:52,920
Inside and outside the play, we recalled our youth.

16
00:02:53,360 --> 00:02:55,680
The night wind hastened tears, drying the red makeup.

17
00:02:56,440 --> 00:02:57,280
In the end,

18
00:02:58,000 --> 00:02:59,720
it caused the singer

19
00:02:59,920 --> 00:03:01,120
to catch a cold in the throat.

20
00:03:01,640 --> 00:03:02,800
And the listener's

21
00:03:03,120 --> 00:03:04,560
eyes turned into wind-chime tears.

22
00:03:06,600 --> 00:03:08,720
No wonder His Majesty, at the morning court today,

23
00:03:09,040 --> 00:03:11,440
was in much better spirits than the past few days.

24
00:03:11,840 --> 00:03:13,640
So it was due to Your Highness's efforts.

25
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:17,440
But last night, I listened to *Injustice to Dou E*.

26
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:19,160
Perhaps because of my age,

27
00:03:19,640 --> 00:03:20,720
I actually tasted something

28
00:03:20,720 --> 00:03:23,000
that was not usually in the script.

29
00:03:25,920 --> 00:03:26,720
Your Highness,

30
00:03:27,320 --> 00:03:28,520
actually, what you like

31
00:03:28,720 --> 00:03:30,480
are not Guan Hanqing's pieces.

32
00:03:31,040 --> 00:03:33,160
Ma Zhiyuan's suit you better.

33
00:03:33,640 --> 00:03:35,480
Like last night's *Autumn in the Han Palace*.

34
00:03:36,240 --> 00:03:38,680
His Majesty must have coaxed you quite a bit.

35
00:03:39,520 --> 00:03:40,600
As the saying goes:

36
00:03:40,880 --> 00:03:41,880
"Fame and profit exhausted,

37
00:03:42,200 --> 00:03:43,320
rights and wrongs ceased.

38
00:03:44,080 --> 00:03:46,120
Red dust is not provoked at the door,

39
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:49,000
green trees prefer to shade the house corner.

40
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:51,720
Green mountains fill the gaps in the wall.

41
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:54,360
Bamboo fences and thatched cottages."

42
00:04:05,360 --> 00:04:07,640
It seems the people in my palace

43
00:04:07,720 --> 00:04:09,520
have received much care from Director Shang.

44
00:04:11,640 --> 00:04:13,440
They are all gifts of sincerity.

45
00:04:17,680 --> 00:04:18,320
I wonder,

46
00:04:18,600 --> 00:04:20,760
if the Eastern Depot's green trees and bamboo fences

47
00:04:21,440 --> 00:04:23,680
can cover up the Western Depot's rights and wrongs?

48
00:04:26,520 --> 00:04:27,480
Imperial Noble Consort,

49
00:04:29,080 --> 00:04:29,880
the Embroidered Uniform Guard,

50
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:30,840
the Eastern Depot,

51
00:04:30,840 --> 00:04:31,680
and the Western Depot,

52
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:33,920
are of the same breath and branch.

53
00:04:34,280 --> 00:04:35,880
We have always sought revenge for the smallest grievance.

54
00:04:36,520 --> 00:04:38,040
We never suffer in silence.

55
00:04:39,200 --> 00:04:40,040
Besides,

56
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:43,520
singing on the blade's edge,

57
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:45,440
one must be prepared

58
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:47,280
to die without a burial place.

59
00:04:48,400 --> 00:04:49,400
Don't you agree?

60
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:25,840
Poisoning. Assassination.

61
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:28,200
Do not disturb the commoners in the city.

62
00:05:28,760 --> 00:05:30,960
Kill them all, leave no one alive.

63
00:05:38,600 --> 00:05:39,240
Yi'er.

64
00:05:39,880 --> 00:05:40,440
Yi'er.

65
00:05:40,760 --> 00:05:41,280
Yi'er.

66
00:05:43,800 --> 00:05:44,160
Get up, quickly.

67
00:05:45,240 --> 00:05:45,640
Go.

68
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:47,760
Yi'er.

69
00:05:48,760 --> 00:05:50,280
No matter what happens later,

70
00:05:50,320 --> 00:05:51,480
you must not make a sound.

71
00:05:52,200 --> 00:05:53,120
As long as you live,

72
00:05:53,440 --> 00:05:54,320
that is more important than anything.

73
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:55,240
Do you understand?

74
00:05:57,480 --> 00:05:58,400
Ten years ago,

75
00:05:59,000 --> 00:05:59,920
the capital was plagued by

76
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:02,120
cases where officials or commoners

77
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:04,720
had their entire families slaughtered overnight.

78
00:06:06,240 --> 00:06:06,840
In the end,

79
00:06:07,440 --> 00:06:08,240
the Eastern Depot

80
00:06:08,320 --> 00:06:10,880
covered up the truth with the excuse of a Fox Demon Manifestation.

81
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:12,800
The solution

82
00:06:13,080 --> 00:06:14,520
was merely to invite Master Konghui to perform rituals

83
00:06:14,760 --> 00:06:15,800
to suppress the demons.

84
00:06:17,160 --> 00:06:18,240
The family extermination cases in the capital

85
00:06:18,320 --> 00:06:19,600
were hastily concluded like this.

86
00:06:20,240 --> 00:06:22,960
The truth was self-evident to the people of the capital.

87
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:25,160
Desperadoes of the capital,

88
00:06:25,520 --> 00:06:26,240
swindling money,

89
00:06:26,440 --> 00:06:27,160
harboring grudges,

90
00:06:27,920 --> 00:06:29,600
regarded the Eastern Depot as their den.

91
00:06:30,200 --> 00:06:31,440
How absurd.

92
00:06:35,600 --> 00:06:36,640
Young master,

93
00:06:36,840 --> 00:06:38,240
in your fate, with this old monk,

94
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:41,200
there is a chance of survival from desperation.

95
00:06:42,840 --> 00:06:44,360
Returning to Linggu Temple with me

96
00:06:44,560 --> 00:06:46,160
would still be a dead end.

97
00:06:49,400 --> 00:06:51,280
If you wish to live,

98
00:06:52,560 --> 00:06:56,240
you must toil and suffer in the streets,

99
00:06:56,840 --> 00:06:58,240
endure hardships to plot revenge,

100
00:06:58,600 --> 00:07:00,160
to settle debts of gratitude and vengeance.

101
00:07:00,600 --> 00:07:02,840
Endure humiliation and survive for three years.

102
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:04,880
Three years,

103
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:07,040
and another three years.

104
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:13,880
Ten years of grudges to break the pagoda.

105
00:07:14,760 --> 00:07:18,360
Zhang Yi will never forget Master's life-saving grace in this life.

106
00:08:10,120 --> 00:08:11,720
Someone save me.

107
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:15,840
Can I really keep living?

108
00:08:18,760 --> 00:08:20,440
Father, I want to save him.

109
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:23,040
There are many beggars in the world.

110
00:08:23,280 --> 00:08:24,600
Are you going to save every one you see?

111
00:08:24,760 --> 00:08:25,960
I am the Young Master of the Tang Clan.

112
00:08:26,120 --> 00:08:27,760
I will be the number one swordsman in the Jianghu.

113
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:29,200
To do what one loathes,

114
00:08:29,320 --> 00:08:30,720
to help others in their need,

115
00:08:30,880 --> 00:08:31,840
is to be a hero.

116
00:08:32,280 --> 00:08:34,800
My name, Tang Xi, will surely be famous throughout the world.

117
00:08:34,920 --> 00:08:36,040
Awing the Jianghu.

118
00:08:37,720 --> 00:08:39,120
Pointing my sword at the sky with a laugh,

119
00:08:39,320 --> 00:08:40,640
Heaven pities the talent of a hero.

120
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:42,160
It is destiny.

121
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:44,800
Konghui truly did not deceive me.

122
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:45,720
Child,

123
00:08:46,400 --> 00:08:47,480
you are not meant to die yet.

124
00:08:47,800 --> 00:08:49,200
And you have formed a bond with my Tang Clan.

125
00:08:50,160 --> 00:08:52,640
I will send someone to teach you the ways to settle down and survive.

126
00:08:53,360 --> 00:08:54,440
As for the future,

127
00:08:54,920 --> 00:08:56,560
it depends on your own luck.

128
00:08:56,720 --> 00:08:57,120
One.

129
00:08:57,440 --> 00:08:57,920
Kill!

130
00:08:59,000 --> 00:08:59,480
Two.

131
00:08:59,800 --> 00:09:00,320
Kill!

132
00:09:01,240 --> 00:09:01,760
Three.

133
00:09:02,000 --> 00:09:03,760
Kill! Kill! Kill!

134
00:09:15,520 --> 00:09:16,080
Ready.

135
00:09:17,760 --> 00:09:18,240
Fire!

136
00:09:19,440 --> 00:09:19,720
Fire!

137
00:09:19,720 --> 00:09:20,840
With the help of the Tang Clan,

138
00:09:21,520 --> 00:09:23,000
my household registration was changed to a respectable status.

139
00:09:23,960 --> 00:09:24,880
I apprenticed to learn skills,

140
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:27,160
joined the Divine Machine Battalion to fight on the battlefield,

141
00:09:27,800 --> 00:09:29,560
and gained the chance to kill the traitor with my own hands.

142
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:38,200
I, Zhang Yi,

143
00:09:38,440 --> 00:09:39,200
greet the General.

144
00:09:44,240 --> 00:09:44,720
Good.

145
00:09:45,960 --> 00:09:47,280
I have long heard of your reputation for bravery.

146
00:09:47,600 --> 00:09:48,440
Seeing you today,

147
00:09:48,640 --> 00:09:49,720
what a fine, eight-foot tall,

148
00:09:49,840 --> 00:09:51,280
heroic and spirited young man.

149
00:09:52,880 --> 00:09:53,600
Strategist Lu,

150
00:09:54,240 --> 00:09:54,920
take a look.

151
00:09:55,560 --> 00:09:57,840
He is even a bit more handsome than you.

152
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:00,400
General, please do not tease me.

153
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:02,880
Adjutant Zhang entered our Divine Machine Battalion on his own merit.

154
00:10:03,520 --> 00:10:04,760
Looking closely today,

155
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:06,320
it is indeed as Master Konghui

156
00:10:06,480 --> 00:10:08,160
teased when recommending him to the Divine Machine Battalion,

157
00:10:08,640 --> 00:10:11,080
that we should keep the girls around the camp

158
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:12,160
under close watch.

159
00:10:19,760 --> 00:10:21,720
General, your chess skills have improved greatly.

160
00:10:23,960 --> 00:10:24,520
Warfare

161
00:10:24,760 --> 00:10:25,440
is the way of deception.

162
00:10:26,080 --> 00:10:27,160
Make the real appear false.

163
00:10:27,240 --> 00:10:28,280
Make the false appear real.

164
00:10:28,800 --> 00:10:31,520
Though I lack your training from Master Konghui,

165
00:10:31,520 --> 00:10:32,560
so exquisite and profound,

166
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:35,040
yet from the art of war,

167
00:10:35,720 --> 00:10:37,080
I can still grasp a thing or two.

168
00:10:37,200 --> 00:10:38,360
Master Konghui's chess skills

169
00:10:38,360 --> 00:10:39,400
are truly exemplary.

170
00:10:44,200 --> 00:10:45,400
General. Lord Zhang.

171
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:46,800
Strategist Lu.

172
00:10:47,240 --> 00:10:49,080
This is an urgent letter from your home in the capital.

173
00:10:55,440 --> 00:10:56,120
There is good news in the family

174
00:10:56,760 --> 00:10:57,640
There is good news in the family!

175
00:10:58,040 --> 00:11:00,760
What makes our usually steady Strategist

176
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:02,000
so pleasantly surprised?

177
00:11:02,240 --> 00:11:02,840
Reporting, General,

178
00:11:03,280 --> 00:11:03,960
it is great news.

179
00:11:07,440 --> 00:11:08,080
A letter from home says

180
00:11:08,280 --> 00:11:09,840
my wife is over three months pregnant.

181
00:11:10,320 --> 00:11:11,440
The pregnancy is stable now,

182
00:11:11,520 --> 00:11:12,560
and she hopes I finish the campaign

183
00:11:12,680 --> 00:11:13,400
and return home soon.

184
00:11:14,280 --> 00:11:15,400
Don't look at our Strategist Lu,

185
00:11:15,400 --> 00:11:16,920
who usually looks like a weak,

186
00:11:16,920 --> 00:11:17,760
pale-faced scholar.

187
00:11:17,960 --> 00:11:19,040
When it comes to the critical moment,

188
00:11:19,080 --> 00:11:20,960
he is a real man who doesn't mess around!

189
00:11:21,400 --> 00:11:22,840
Married for just over three months,

190
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:23,920
and he's already reaping the harvest,

191
00:11:23,960 --> 00:11:24,880
getting exactly what he planted.

192
00:11:25,040 --> 00:11:26,080
No wonder Strategist Lu,

193
00:11:26,080 --> 00:11:27,240
during the march a few days ago,

194
00:11:27,400 --> 00:11:28,560
walked like a swaying willow

195
00:11:28,680 --> 00:11:29,640
with his calves trembling.

196
00:11:29,880 --> 00:11:31,040
Your efforts were not in vain!

197
00:11:32,160 --> 00:11:33,160
You kid,

198
00:11:33,280 --> 00:11:34,920
you're thirty and still not married.

199
00:11:35,280 --> 00:11:36,200
Spending all day in the barracks

200
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:37,760
hanging out with those old soldiers.

201
00:11:38,120 --> 00:11:39,960
I wonder which girl would take you on.

202
00:11:40,240 --> 00:11:41,000
Get lost.

203
00:11:42,760 --> 00:11:45,040
Strategist Lu, your news isn't up to date.

204
00:11:45,400 --> 00:11:46,520
There actually is a woman

205
00:11:46,760 --> 00:11:48,840
who likes Zhang Yi's unreliable ways.

206
00:11:49,280 --> 00:11:50,680
Don't tell me, I know.

207
00:11:51,200 --> 00:11:52,120
It seems to be

208
00:11:52,800 --> 00:11:54,080
Cook Zhang's sister, right?

209
00:11:54,600 --> 00:11:55,040
Zhang Yi,

210
00:11:55,360 --> 00:11:55,800
if you ask me,

211
00:11:55,960 --> 00:11:58,040
that girl is truly devoted to you.

212
00:11:58,320 --> 00:11:58,680
Why don't you

213
00:11:58,800 --> 00:12:00,160
just accept that girl?

214
00:12:00,400 --> 00:12:00,880
In the future,

215
00:12:01,080 --> 00:12:01,920
your two brothers here

216
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:03,080
can benefit from you

217
00:12:03,200 --> 00:12:04,200
and get an extra chicken leg or something.

218
00:12:05,400 --> 00:12:06,280
I say, that's enough from you two.

219
00:12:06,280 --> 00:12:07,040
Stop teasing me.

220
00:12:07,600 --> 00:12:08,360
How do you know

221
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:09,640
I haven't gone to propose?

222
00:12:12,920 --> 00:12:14,440
It's rare for our Zhang Yi

223
00:12:14,720 --> 00:12:15,440
to propose to a girl!

224
00:12:15,880 --> 00:12:16,560
Which family is she from?

225
00:12:16,800 --> 00:12:17,560
How old is she?

226
00:12:17,760 --> 00:12:18,480
Do you have a portrait?

227
00:12:18,640 --> 00:12:19,000
Come on,

228
00:12:19,360 --> 00:12:20,040
let us have a look.

229
00:12:20,600 --> 00:12:22,720
Naturally, I'll be marrying into a family in Shu.

230
00:12:23,320 --> 00:12:23,920
As for anything else,

231
00:12:23,920 --> 00:12:24,880
it's inconvenient for me to say.

232
00:12:25,080 --> 00:12:25,440
Right now,

233
00:12:25,640 --> 00:12:26,560
she's probably out playing.

234
00:12:29,680 --> 00:12:30,960
The road to Shu is difficult,

235
00:12:31,760 --> 00:12:33,480
harder than climbing to the blue sky.

236
00:12:33,800 --> 00:12:35,120
This brat's wife,

237
00:12:35,600 --> 00:12:36,880
I heard, compared to the one from a while back

238
00:12:36,880 --> 00:12:37,640
who caused a scene in the barracks,

239
00:12:37,640 --> 00:12:39,040
the demon king from Minister Yuan's family,

240
00:12:39,320 --> 00:12:40,520
she's even more of a handful.

241
00:12:41,720 --> 00:12:43,760
To marry such a beautiful wife,

242
00:12:45,000 --> 00:12:47,160
one really needs some skill.

243
00:12:48,440 --> 00:12:49,640
Frosty moonlight covers the world,

244
00:12:50,000 --> 00:12:51,040
but there is only one Shuoyue.

245
00:12:52,040 --> 00:12:53,040
My Lady Hua

246
00:12:53,280 --> 00:12:55,080
was also won by me after a thousand pleas.

247
00:12:55,440 --> 00:12:56,320
If you ask me,

248
00:12:56,480 --> 00:12:58,400
people like you who are about to get married,

249
00:12:58,400 --> 00:12:59,480
and those who are already married,

250
00:12:59,840 --> 00:13:00,800
just don't understand the joy

251
00:13:00,840 --> 00:13:01,880
of us unmarried folks.

252
00:13:01,880 --> 00:13:02,640
Right, Brother Fu?

253
00:13:03,360 --> 00:13:03,880
Lord Zhang,

254
00:13:04,320 --> 00:13:05,640
after this battle ends,

255
00:13:06,120 --> 00:13:07,240
I'm going to get married too.

256
00:13:08,120 --> 00:13:09,400
You have such good news too?

257
00:13:11,880 --> 00:13:12,480
My Lord.

258
00:13:13,160 --> 00:13:14,600
I know that as a sleeper agent for the Depot,

259
00:13:15,200 --> 00:13:17,200
wanting to retire breaks the rules.

260
00:13:17,800 --> 00:13:18,840
But I really do not want

261
00:13:18,840 --> 00:13:19,920
to do this kind of business anymore.

262
00:13:20,960 --> 00:13:22,760
If one leaves the Depot,

263
00:13:23,280 --> 00:13:25,640
one must cripple one's own signature skills.

264
00:13:25,960 --> 00:13:27,280
Without your skills,

265
00:13:27,680 --> 00:13:30,280
how will you support yourself in the future?

266
00:13:30,880 --> 00:13:33,240
If I cripple my skills, I can pick them up again.

267
00:13:34,960 --> 00:13:36,240
As long as I am not dead,

268
00:13:36,680 --> 00:13:37,840
the skills will not be lost.

269
00:13:40,000 --> 00:13:42,040
If someone is willing to hit the south wall,

270
00:13:42,520 --> 00:13:44,240
naturally, I will not stop them.

271
00:14:26,680 --> 00:14:27,240
Father

272
00:14:28,600 --> 00:14:29,040
Good

273
00:14:30,160 --> 00:14:32,160
I discussed the dowry patterns with Auntie Zhang

274
00:14:32,400 --> 00:14:33,080
They...

275
00:14:33,280 --> 00:14:34,960
Everyone says Auntie Zhang is a woman of perfect fortune

276
00:14:35,320 --> 00:14:37,440
Her parents and in-laws are all alive,

277
00:14:37,720 --> 00:14:38,600
and she has both sons and daughters

278
00:14:39,280 --> 00:14:40,520
I hope to be like that too

279
00:14:41,320 --> 00:14:42,640
Although I may not have

280
00:14:42,640 --> 00:14:43,760
as much good fortune as Auntie Zhang,

281
00:14:44,600 --> 00:14:45,680
I still hope that

282
00:14:46,400 --> 00:14:47,640
after I marry Brother Fu,

283
00:14:48,240 --> 00:14:49,360
we will have both sons and daughters,

284
00:14:49,840 --> 00:14:51,000
and Father will live a long life

285
00:14:53,680 --> 00:14:54,440
Oh, you

286
00:14:56,360 --> 00:14:58,920
If you had married Scholar Zhang,

287
00:15:09,600 --> 00:15:11,040
this wish of yours

288
00:15:12,080 --> 00:15:14,320
would most likely have come true

289
00:15:15,200 --> 00:15:16,360
But instead, it just had to be

290
00:15:16,880 --> 00:15:18,520
that silly boy from the hunter's family

291
00:15:21,360 --> 00:15:23,120
If he were a handsome young man in green robes,

292
00:15:23,720 --> 00:15:26,040
I'd assume you were blinded by love,

293
00:15:26,680 --> 00:15:27,520
but at least your eyes weren't blind

294
00:15:27,960 --> 00:15:28,920
But that thing...

295
00:15:30,400 --> 00:15:31,360
He looks so dull and stupid,

296
00:15:31,480 --> 00:15:33,200
dark as a lump of coal

297
00:15:35,120 --> 00:15:35,960
What do you expect me to say

298
00:15:36,440 --> 00:15:37,840
Don't speak about Brother Fu like that

299
00:15:38,920 --> 00:15:40,440
We are already betrothed

300
00:15:41,160 --> 00:15:42,520
No matter how much you dislike him,

301
00:15:42,760 --> 00:15:44,200
he is still my future husband

302
00:15:44,440 --> 00:15:45,400
and your son-in-law

303
00:15:46,360 --> 00:15:47,040
Besides,

304
00:15:47,960 --> 00:15:50,280
you've eaten plenty of the wild rabbit meat he sent

305
00:15:51,360 --> 00:15:53,360
If he stopped providing me with wild rabbit meat,

306
00:15:54,040 --> 00:15:55,600
what redeeming qualities would he have left

307
00:15:56,520 --> 00:15:57,400
Only you

308
00:15:57,800 --> 00:15:59,840
would be so dead set on marrying him

309
00:16:00,400 --> 00:16:01,560
From the bottom of my heart,

310
00:16:01,600 --> 00:16:03,040
I did not want to agree to this marriage

311
00:16:07,760 --> 00:16:11,160
A Rank 6 Captain in the Divine Machine Battalion...

312
00:16:13,000 --> 00:16:14,680
The title sounds nice,

313
00:16:15,560 --> 00:16:17,560
but they live with their heads on the line

314
00:16:19,200 --> 00:16:21,560
Have you heard the opera "Women Generals of the Yang Family"

315
00:16:22,280 --> 00:16:23,120
Once war breaks out,

316
00:16:24,200 --> 00:16:25,320
you get married today,

317
00:16:25,960 --> 00:16:27,560
and become a widow tomorrow

318
00:16:28,920 --> 00:16:30,400
If that's how it is for generals,

319
00:16:31,480 --> 00:16:32,560
what about a common soldier

320
00:16:34,280 --> 00:16:35,160
If you ask me,

321
00:16:36,920 --> 00:16:38,280
he'd be better off coming back to be a hunter

322
00:16:40,240 --> 00:16:41,200
You're not allowed to say that about him

323
00:16:41,760 --> 00:16:42,880
You were the one who said,

324
00:16:43,280 --> 00:16:44,760
"If a man does not display his soaring ambitions,

325
00:16:45,240 --> 00:16:46,720
he wastes his God-given eight-foot frame"

326
00:16:47,120 --> 00:16:48,760
Brother Fu's ambition is to join the Divine Machine Battalion

327
00:16:48,760 --> 00:16:50,480
to fight on the battlefield and defend the country

328
00:16:50,760 --> 00:16:51,800
How come when it comes to you,

329
00:16:52,760 --> 00:16:53,920
you're finding fault with it again

330
00:16:56,680 --> 00:16:57,040
Come

331
00:16:57,640 --> 00:16:58,040
Come here

332
00:17:21,880 --> 00:17:23,320
It is Dad who has failed you

333
00:17:28,440 --> 00:17:31,280
Letting you lose your mother so early

334
00:17:32,240 --> 00:17:34,920
And ruining your beautiful face

335
00:17:37,960 --> 00:17:39,320
Finally

336
00:17:40,480 --> 00:17:42,800
And finding a son-in-law I don't like

337
00:17:44,920 --> 00:17:45,720
Dad

338
00:17:46,600 --> 00:17:47,400
Dad

339
00:17:48,760 --> 00:17:50,240
I have chosen Brother Fu

340
00:17:50,880 --> 00:17:53,160
We grew up together as childhood sweethearts

341
00:17:53,520 --> 00:17:54,640
I have set my heart on him

342
00:17:55,240 --> 00:17:55,800
By the way

343
00:17:56,080 --> 00:17:57,480
Brother Fu and I have already discussed it

344
00:17:57,880 --> 00:17:58,840
After we get married

345
00:17:59,280 --> 00:18:01,200
We'll build another room in his family's yard

346
00:18:02,080 --> 00:18:03,440
We'll bring you over to live with us

347
00:18:03,720 --> 00:18:04,440
We won't separate the family

348
00:18:05,560 --> 00:18:06,800
That's not proper

349
00:18:08,200 --> 00:18:08,880
You tell him

350
00:18:09,400 --> 00:18:11,680
Build two small rooms, east and west

351
00:18:12,880 --> 00:18:13,720
I have a lot of stuff

352
00:18:14,200 --> 00:18:14,840
It won't fit otherwise

353
00:18:20,280 --> 00:18:21,240
Come in

354
00:18:23,520 --> 00:18:24,480
Greetings, Father-in-law

355
00:18:26,800 --> 00:18:27,560
Why are you here?

356
00:18:28,280 --> 00:18:29,840
This is a pheasant I just hunted this morning

357
00:18:30,080 --> 00:18:31,240
For Father-in-law to have a treat

358
00:18:31,680 --> 00:18:33,280
You're leaving in three hours

359
00:18:33,680 --> 00:18:35,200
Why bother with these useless chores?

360
00:18:35,520 --> 00:18:36,840
Isn't it just to make Father-in-law

361
00:18:37,120 --> 00:18:38,200
Look at me more favorably?

362
00:18:38,960 --> 00:18:39,840
I'm leaving

363
00:18:40,480 --> 00:18:41,200
So that Father-in-law

364
00:18:41,200 --> 00:18:43,240
Will speak well of me to you

365
00:18:43,960 --> 00:18:44,360
Oh, right

366
00:18:44,920 --> 00:18:46,280
General Lin Feng has already promised me

367
00:18:46,600 --> 00:18:47,320
When I return this time

368
00:18:47,400 --> 00:18:48,560
He will host our wedding

369
00:18:49,040 --> 00:18:50,960
I'll marry you in grand style then

370
00:18:51,200 --> 00:18:52,280
I definitely won't let you suffer any slight

371
00:18:53,560 --> 00:18:54,360
I didn't expect

372
00:18:54,640 --> 00:18:56,680
To have the chance to meet a great hero

373
00:18:57,040 --> 00:18:57,560
That's impressive

374
00:19:02,320 --> 00:19:02,760
So beautiful

375
00:19:04,560 --> 00:19:05,720
Don't apply this stuff anymore

376
00:19:06,000 --> 00:19:07,000
All medicine is partly poison

377
00:19:07,960 --> 00:19:10,480
Our love doesn't depend on this

378
00:19:10,920 --> 00:19:12,480
To marry my childhood sweetheart

379
00:19:13,080 --> 00:19:14,840
Is a blessing I earned over three lifetimes

380
00:19:23,200 --> 00:19:24,000
You two

381
00:19:26,200 --> 00:19:27,240
That's enough

382
00:19:28,120 --> 00:19:29,240
You aren't even married yet

383
00:19:29,720 --> 00:19:30,760
Even if you were married

384
00:19:31,400 --> 00:19:32,960
You're not allowed to do this in front of me

385
00:19:38,080 --> 00:19:39,600
But I'm still worried

386
00:19:42,000 --> 00:19:42,880
Take this

387
00:19:44,080 --> 00:19:45,560
This is the peace charm my parents

388
00:19:45,640 --> 00:19:47,680
Obtained from Master Konghui

389
00:19:48,240 --> 00:19:49,400
I've worn it since I was a child

390
00:19:49,720 --> 00:19:50,560
Now you take it

391
00:19:51,960 --> 00:19:53,160
Think of it as me being with you

392
00:19:53,560 --> 00:19:54,200
Crazy girl

393
00:19:54,760 --> 00:19:55,920
Such a spiritual object

394
00:19:55,920 --> 00:19:57,040
How can you just give it away?

395
00:19:57,360 --> 00:19:57,840
Get it back for me

396
00:19:57,840 --> 00:19:58,360
No

397
00:19:58,680 --> 00:19:59,480
He is my life

398
00:20:03,720 --> 00:20:04,360
I'll wait for you

399
00:20:05,320 --> 00:20:06,160
Come back safely

400
00:20:06,400 --> 00:20:07,360
I will return

401
00:20:29,600 --> 00:20:30,240
Director Shang,

402
00:20:31,040 --> 00:20:33,160
the Divine Machine Battalion is about to deploy.

403
00:20:33,600 --> 00:20:34,440
Before I leave,

404
00:20:34,680 --> 00:20:35,760
I have a personal matter to settle.

405
00:20:39,320 --> 00:20:40,320
This is the betrothal gift prepared

406
00:20:40,400 --> 00:20:42,640
according to the General's Manor's rules for the lady of the house.

407
00:20:43,440 --> 00:20:44,120
Shuoyue...

408
00:20:44,200 --> 00:20:45,960
I paid to redeem her from Blossom Pavilion.

409
00:20:46,640 --> 00:20:47,960
I already know the reasons behind it.

410
00:20:48,840 --> 00:20:50,240
As the General of the Divine Machine Battalion,

411
00:20:50,680 --> 00:20:51,840
I should not accept favors

412
00:20:51,840 --> 00:20:52,800
for no reason.

413
00:20:53,440 --> 00:20:54,600
Since she is your daughter,

414
00:20:55,040 --> 00:20:56,000
proper etiquette must be observed.

415
00:20:56,840 --> 00:20:58,040
The dignity due to a bride

416
00:20:58,840 --> 00:20:59,720
must be upheld.

417
00:21:03,880 --> 00:21:04,840
General Lin,

418
00:21:05,680 --> 00:21:07,160
the fact that you came to find me today

419
00:21:07,680 --> 00:21:09,080
proves that Miss Shuoyue

420
00:21:09,200 --> 00:21:10,480
has already laid her cards on the table.

421
00:21:11,200 --> 00:21:12,600
She has followed me for twenty years.

422
00:21:12,920 --> 00:21:14,160
I view her as my own flesh and blood.

423
00:21:14,600 --> 00:21:17,520
Though placed in Blossom Pavilion as the top courtesan,

424
00:21:17,960 --> 00:21:20,120
her nature is like a wild beast,

425
00:21:21,040 --> 00:21:22,600
and she needs no sympathy from men.

426
00:21:23,760 --> 00:21:26,320
To win Lady Hua's affection,

427
00:21:27,440 --> 00:21:28,240
General Lin,

428
00:21:29,240 --> 00:21:30,480
you are quite capable indeed.

429
00:21:31,080 --> 00:21:32,720
Treating a remarkable woman like Shuoyue

430
00:21:33,120 --> 00:21:34,640
with respect and freedom,

431
00:21:34,760 --> 00:21:36,880
her heart will naturally find its home.

432
00:21:37,560 --> 00:21:38,320
Director Shang,

433
00:21:38,440 --> 00:21:40,360
if one truly viewed Shuoyue as one's own,

434
00:21:40,920 --> 00:21:43,600
and not as a capable guard of the Eastern Depot,

435
00:21:43,960 --> 00:21:44,920
would one be at a loss

436
00:21:45,240 --> 00:21:46,200
because of her tears,

437
00:21:46,440 --> 00:21:47,400
and yield to her every wish?

438
00:21:51,040 --> 00:21:53,920
She is merely acting on the surface,

439
00:21:54,240 --> 00:21:55,200
putting on a show.

440
00:21:56,080 --> 00:21:58,040
Possessing true resources and power

441
00:21:58,400 --> 00:22:00,000
is the foundation of her survival.

442
00:22:01,600 --> 00:22:03,640
Director Shang teaches his daughter well, indeed.

443
00:22:04,200 --> 00:22:05,600
The world's upbringing of women

444
00:22:05,640 --> 00:22:07,520
mostly aims for good wives and loving mothers,

445
00:22:07,760 --> 00:22:09,000
with marriage as their mission.

446
00:22:09,560 --> 00:22:10,600
Music, chess, calligraphy, and painting

447
00:22:10,720 --> 00:22:13,080
are but requirements for noble ladies.

448
00:22:14,080 --> 00:22:14,960
Throughout their lives,

449
00:22:15,120 --> 00:22:16,120
it is boring and repetitive,

450
00:22:16,240 --> 00:22:17,120
without any clue.

451
00:22:17,520 --> 00:22:19,520
But Shuoyue is a magnificent flower herself,

452
00:22:20,080 --> 00:22:21,240
truly fascinating.

453
00:22:24,240 --> 00:22:25,120
General Lin,

454
00:22:25,320 --> 00:22:28,120
if you sincerely wish to marry Miss Shuoyue,

455
00:22:28,480 --> 00:22:29,040
then

456
00:22:29,520 --> 00:22:30,600
I will marry her to you as

457
00:22:30,880 --> 00:22:34,040
the legitimate daughter of the Left Chief Censor.

458
00:22:34,560 --> 00:22:37,400
This way, no one in the court will criticize you,

459
00:22:38,080 --> 00:22:39,840
and your future career

460
00:22:40,320 --> 00:22:41,600
will not be affected.

461
00:22:44,160 --> 00:22:46,200
I have already considered this matter carefully.

462
00:22:46,920 --> 00:22:49,040
Since I have chosen Lady Hua as my wife,

463
00:22:49,720 --> 00:22:51,480
why should I care about her background?

464
00:22:51,840 --> 00:22:52,720
After we are married,

465
00:22:53,080 --> 00:22:54,720
I will take her to the Western frontier,

466
00:22:54,880 --> 00:22:55,760
or the southern seas.

467
00:22:56,000 --> 00:22:56,680
I will fight to earn her

468
00:22:56,720 --> 00:22:58,360
the respectable title of Lady of Imperial Mandate.

469
00:22:58,720 --> 00:23:00,160
We will live freely as husband and wife.

470
00:23:00,360 --> 00:23:02,120
Why care about the opinions of others?

471
00:23:02,840 --> 00:23:03,600
Good.

472
00:23:04,360 --> 00:23:08,080
General Lin is truly a man of insight and character.

473
00:23:08,560 --> 00:23:10,000
I will follow your rules

474
00:23:10,320 --> 00:23:12,800
and send Lady Hua to your manor.

475
00:23:13,320 --> 00:23:13,960
Director Shang,

476
00:23:14,520 --> 00:23:15,720
military affairs are pressing,

477
00:23:16,200 --> 00:23:17,400
so I will not disturb you further.

478
00:23:21,000 --> 00:23:21,840
General Lin,

479
00:23:22,480 --> 00:23:23,960
with the Oirat invasion this time,

480
00:23:24,360 --> 00:23:27,280
we rely on your hard work and effort.

481
00:23:29,000 --> 00:23:29,640
Director Shang,

482
00:23:30,200 --> 00:23:32,000
since a true man pledges his life to his country

483
00:23:32,160 --> 00:23:32,960
and to his confidant,

484
00:23:33,440 --> 00:23:35,400
he can only serve until death.

485
00:23:36,040 --> 00:23:37,000
Protecting the country

486
00:23:37,080 --> 00:23:39,160
is the duty of every man of Great Ming.

487
00:23:40,000 --> 00:23:40,760
Shuoyue

488
00:23:40,960 --> 00:23:42,560
also likes me this way.

489
00:23:57,080 --> 00:23:57,560
General.

490
00:23:57,600 --> 00:23:58,080
General.

491
00:23:59,320 --> 00:24:00,800
Those remarks just now were truly inappropriate.

492
00:24:01,080 --> 00:24:01,960
The army is about to depart.

493
00:24:01,960 --> 00:24:03,680
For you to be so open with the Eastern Depot now,

494
00:24:03,680 --> 00:24:04,720
was truly a bit rash.

495
00:24:05,040 --> 00:24:07,080
In court now, the Depots and Guards sow discord and frame others.

496
00:24:07,200 --> 00:24:08,160
Many have been stripped of their command because of it.

497
00:24:08,160 --> 00:24:08,840
If, this time,

498
00:24:09,600 --> 00:24:10,840
to demonstrate my loyalty,

499
00:24:11,040 --> 00:24:12,000
upon my triumphant return,

500
00:24:12,200 --> 00:24:13,640
I will resign to His Majesty and retire.

501
00:24:13,960 --> 00:24:15,880
There is no need to say more about the rest.

502
00:24:16,600 --> 00:24:17,600
Wherever you go, General, I will follow.

503
00:24:18,240 --> 00:24:19,720
Just do not leave us two brothers behind.

504
00:24:20,240 --> 00:24:20,600
Good.

505
00:24:21,640 --> 00:24:22,280
Good brothers.

506
00:25:00,440 --> 00:25:02,480
You witnessed it just now.

507
00:25:03,520 --> 00:25:05,880
With General Lin's courage and insight,

508
00:25:06,640 --> 00:25:08,600
winning Lady Hua's favor

509
00:25:09,000 --> 00:25:09,800
is hardly surprising.

510
00:25:11,440 --> 00:25:14,200
He has the makings of a peerless hero,

511
00:25:14,760 --> 00:25:16,440
and in the imperial court,

512
00:25:16,760 --> 00:25:18,480
he handles matters with sincerity.

513
00:25:19,080 --> 00:25:20,840
He is definitely no boorish warrior.

514
00:25:21,720 --> 00:25:23,960
If he were merely a capable general of the state,

515
00:25:24,680 --> 00:25:25,560
why would you need to

516
00:25:25,560 --> 00:25:27,360
go to such lengths to send Lady Hua to approach him?

517
00:25:28,720 --> 00:25:29,760
After all,

518
00:25:30,440 --> 00:25:31,600
he is the General of the Great Ming's

519
00:25:31,600 --> 00:25:33,560
Divine Machine Battalion, the only firearms division.

520
00:25:34,600 --> 00:25:37,800
Saltpeter, cannons, muskets, rockets, fire caltrops,

521
00:25:38,120 --> 00:25:39,040
large and small iron guns,

522
00:25:39,200 --> 00:25:39,800
and divine machine arrows.

523
00:25:40,560 --> 00:25:42,040
Possessing such military power,

524
00:25:42,280 --> 00:25:44,840
one would be invincible even with few soldiers.

525
00:25:45,360 --> 00:25:48,000
Who wouldn't want a piece of that prize?

526
00:25:50,000 --> 00:25:53,000
But Lin Feng is too upright and independent,

527
00:25:53,880 --> 00:25:54,960
and difficult to control.

528
00:25:56,080 --> 00:25:57,160
I originally thought

529
00:25:57,760 --> 00:25:59,840
your efforts were merely in vain.

530
00:26:01,640 --> 00:26:02,640
But who would have guessed,

531
00:26:03,560 --> 00:26:04,560
you made a deal

532
00:26:04,560 --> 00:26:06,360
that cost you both the lady and the army.

533
00:26:16,480 --> 00:26:17,800
Beautiful flowers

534
00:26:18,600 --> 00:26:21,120
will eventually wither and fall.

535
00:26:22,200 --> 00:26:24,960
This is also the fate of living things.

536
00:26:27,040 --> 00:26:29,160
I would rather suffer eight hundred losses

537
00:26:29,520 --> 00:26:31,480
to inflict a thousand on the enemy.

538
00:26:31,880 --> 00:26:33,080
To keep it forever

539
00:26:33,200 --> 00:26:36,280
frozen in its moment of greatest bloom

540
00:26:39,360 --> 00:26:40,840
is also understandable.

541
00:26:42,560 --> 00:26:43,840
Flowers will wither.

542
00:26:44,360 --> 00:26:45,560
The moon begins its cycle,

543
00:26:46,080 --> 00:26:47,360
going round and round.

544
00:26:49,640 --> 00:26:52,360
How could I allow such barbarians to pick it?

545
00:26:54,040 --> 00:26:54,640
However,

546
00:26:55,360 --> 00:26:56,880
the Divine Machine Battalion, in the end,

547
00:26:57,320 --> 00:26:59,400
still needs my Western Depot to step in.

548
00:27:00,120 --> 00:27:01,200
If Lin Feng wants to blame someone,

549
00:27:02,560 --> 00:27:05,400
he should blame "pride invites loss, humility receives benefit."

550
00:27:05,640 --> 00:27:06,960
It is truly the way of Heaven.

551
00:27:07,760 --> 00:27:08,600
This time,

552
00:27:10,240 --> 00:27:11,680
no one can help him.

553
00:27:17,760 --> 00:27:18,600
For this campaign,

554
00:27:19,000 --> 00:27:21,920
Director Wang Zhi has brought reinforcements on behalf of His Majesty.

555
00:27:22,480 --> 00:27:23,400
For us,

556
00:27:23,760 --> 00:27:25,600
it is truly like help from the gods.

557
00:27:26,040 --> 00:27:27,200
Although I am an inner official,

558
00:27:27,600 --> 00:27:28,520
and in these years,

559
00:27:28,640 --> 00:27:30,040
I have often led troops in battle

560
00:27:30,160 --> 00:27:31,240
and achieved distinguished merits,

561
00:27:32,040 --> 00:27:32,960
compared to the General,

562
00:27:33,240 --> 00:27:34,520
I am still far behind.

563
00:27:35,680 --> 00:27:36,800
Coming to aid this time,

